When the vehicle overtook you,

00:27:16.120 --> 00:27:17.320
the two vehicles collided.

00:27:18.440 --> 00:27:19.479
Because you were scared,

00:27:19.480 --> 00:27:20.559
you didn't stop.

00:27:20.560 --> 00:27:21.760
You drove straight home.

00:27:21.960 --> 00:27:24.160
When you got home, you didn't tell anyone.

