The victim is not homeless,

00:28:24.080 --> 00:28:25.399
but part of the Han family,

00:28:25.400 --> 00:28:26.479
Han Kui Long's son,

00:28:26.480 --> 00:28:27.480
Han Gang.

00:28:27.840 --> 00:28:28.920
Stop. Time out.

00:28:30.040 --> 00:28:31.839
I need to talk to my client.

00:28:31.840 --> 00:28:33.320
Don't ask any more questions.

00:28:48.120 --> 00:28:49.120
Judge Qin.

00:28:51.760 --> 00:28:53.280
I heard your son turned himself in.

00:28:59.240 --> 00:29:01.320
I'm the one who applied for the exit ban.

