00:29:09.360 --> 00:29:10.560
I always thought...

00:29:11.160 --> 00:29:13.440
you were the wisest person among everyone I knew.

00:29:14.360 --> 00:29:15.559
I didn't think you'd do...

00:29:15.560 --> 00:29:16.680
something so foolish.

00:29:18.720 --> 00:29:19.720
This is...

00:29:19.960 --> 00:29:21.760
the DNA test result.

00:29:22.600 --> 00:29:23.919
The saliva sample...

00:29:23.920 --> 00:29:25.920
from the asthma inhaler found at the accident scene...

00:29:26.080 --> 00:29:27.159
and the DNA of the suspect...

00:29:27.160 --> 00:29:28.320
I've been investigating recently...

00:29:28.880 --> 00:29:29.960
are a perfect match.

00:29:30.520 --> 00:29:31.520
Let me tell you.

00:29:32.400 --> 00:29:33.759
If your evidence collection process...

00:29:33.760 --> 00:29:34.840
was unlawful,

00:29:35.160 --> 00:29:36.520
including stealing my trash,

00:29:36.720 --> 00:29:38.760
it cannot be used as evidence.

00:29:40.240 --> 00:29:41.920
Judge Qin truly lives up to his name.

00:29:42.760 --> 00:29:44.760
Since the suspect has turned himself in,

00:29:45.560 --> 00:29:46.879
I'll apply to take a new sample...

00:29:46.880 --> 00:29:48.320
and for a re-test.

00:29:50.240 --> 00:29:51.320
The result will be the same.

00:30:00.440 --> 00:30:01.440
Wei Wei.

00:30:01.480 --> 00:30:03.840
Why did you lie to Grandma?

00:30:06.560 --> 00:30:08.559
I was afraid that if you knew who I hit,

00:30:08.560 --> 00:30:10.120
you'd stop me from turning myself in.

00:30:12.520 --> 00:30:13.840
I really want to get it off my chest.

00:30:15.040 --> 00:30:17.240
I don't want to drag anyone else into this.

00:30:23.960 --> 00:30:26.120
I... I don't need a lawyer to represent me.

00:30:29.640 --> 00:30:31.720
I just want to take responsibility myself.

00:30:41.960 --> 00:30:42.960
I understand.

00:30:43.560 --> 00:30:44.560
You're all grown up now.

00:30:44.920 --> 00:30:46.440
You can make your own decisions.

00:30:47.360 --> 00:30:48.960
But Grandma will be by your side.

00:30:49.520 --> 00:30:51.080
I will protect your interests...

00:30:51.480 --> 00:30:52.720
within the bounds of the law.

00:30:54.640 --> 00:30:55.720
Don't be afraid.

00:30:59.040 --> 00:31:00.040
Okay.

00:31:00.160 --> 00:31:01.160
Let's resume.

00:31:02.720 --> 00:31:03.720
Continue.

00:31:13.920 --> 00:31:14.920
Yi Wei.

00:31:15.280 --> 00:31:16.920
- Yi Wei! - Judge Qin, you can't do this.

00:31:17.040 --> 00:31:18.040
Let them talk.

00:31:18.040 --> 00:31:19.040
Just let him talk.

00:31:19.600 --> 00:31:20.600
Son.

00:31:21.720 --> 00:31:23.319
It's okay. Don't be afraid.

00:31:23.320 --> 00:31:24.320
Dad's here.

00:31:24.360 --> 00:31:25.360
Dad.

00:31:25.840 --> 00:31:27.400
I told them what happened that day.

00:31:30.040 --> 00:31:31.760
It's all my responsibility.

00:31:32.120 --> 00:31:33.360
It has nothing to do with you.

00:31:37.600 --> 00:31:38.960
What are you charging him with?

00:31:39.320 --> 00:31:41.239
Qin Yi Wei has violated traffic laws...

00:31:41.240 --> 00:31:42.400
and is guilty of evading responsibility.

00:31:42.920 --> 00:31:44.720
We have officially arrested him.

00:31:45.560 --> 00:31:46.560
I want to bail him out.

00:31:46.960 --> 00:31:48.040
Did you apply for bail?

00:31:48.160 --> 00:31:49.519
Do you think I don't know?

00:31:49.520 --> 00:31:50.560
It was rejected.

00:31:50.920 --> 00:31:52.560
Considering the risk of flight,

00:31:53.240 --> 00:31:54.600
he can't be bailed out...

00:31:54.880 --> 00:31:56.120
for the time being.

00:31:56.920 --> 00:31:58.000
We will detain...

00:31:58.360 --> 00:32:00.040
the suspect directly in the detention center.

00:32:05.160 --> 00:32:06.160
Take him away.

00:32:06.360 --> 00:32:07.360
Yes, sir.

00:32:08.080 --> 00:32:09.080
Don't be afraid.

00:32:09.120 --> 00:32:10.160
Dad will think of a way.

00:32:10.520 --> 00:32:11.520
Trust me.

00:32:11.521 --> 00:32:13.120
Trust me. Don't be afraid.

00:32:15.200 --> 00:32:16.200
Trust me.

00:32:18.600 --> 00:32:19.600
Let's go.

00:32:30.920 --> 00:32:32.080
I have something to ask you.

00:32:32.960 --> 00:32:33.960
Let's talk when we get home.

00:32:48.520 --> 00:32:49.520
Tang Xuan.

00:32:54.320 --> 00:32:55.759
Didn't I tell you...

00:32:55.760 --> 00:32:56.760
not to get involved...

00:32:56.761 --> 00:32:59.120
in this case while you're on leave?

00:33:00.840 --> 00:33:02.759
But didn't you help me get an exit ban?

00:33:02.760 --> 00:33:05.240
I gathered intel and took action.

00:33:05.520 --> 00:33:06.919
But you used your police authority...

00:33:06.920 --> 00:33:08.080
without permission.

00:33:08.520 --> 00:33:10.119
Do you think the Internal Investigations Unit...

00:33:10.120 --> 00:33:11.279
doesn't have enough evidence to charge you,

00:33:11.280 --> 00:33:12.880
so you're handing yourself over?

00:33:14.440 --> 00:33:15.440
Yes.

00:33:15.441 --> 00:33:16.560
It's my fault.

00:33:17.240 --> 00:33:19.160
But finding the real culprit is worth it.

00:33:20.680 --> 00:33:21.680
Okay.

00:33:21.681 --> 00:33:23.000
When the case is over,

00:33:23.240 --> 00:33:24.559
I think the Internal Investigations Unit...

00:33:24.560 --> 00:33:25.560
will see that you're capable...

00:33:25.640 --> 00:33:26.640
and that you solved the case,

00:33:26.720 --> 00:33:28.760
so they won't keep going after you.

