The case won't be over so soon.

00:33:30.960 --> 00:33:32.559
Judge Qin has been misleading me.

00:33:32.560 --> 00:33:34.760
Don't cause any more trouble, okay?

00:33:35.160 --> 00:33:36.759
Didn't his son already say...

00:33:36.760 --> 00:33:38.920
his dad didn't know anything?

00:33:39.240 --> 00:33:41.479
Also, you don't have any evidence...

00:33:41.480 --> 00:33:42.519
that Qin Yu was involved.

00:33:42.520 --> 00:33:43.520
If you reinstate me,

00:33:43.521 --> 00:33:44.920
I'll be able to find the evidence.

00:33:45.280 --> 00:33:47.200
Anyway, I've been in charge of this case all along.

00:33:49.680 --> 00:33:51.360
Okay. I'll let you investigate.

00:33:51.720 --> 00:33:52.879
But you have to promise me...

00:33:52.880 --> 00:33:54.400
not to target Qin Yu anymore.

00:33:54.960 --> 00:33:56.359
I don't want others...

00:33:56.360 --> 00:33:58.079
to think you have ulterior motives.

00:33:58.080 --> 00:33:59.080
Do you understand?

00:33:59.760 --> 00:34:01.240
I won't let him off that easily.

00:34:05.200 --> 00:34:06.880
Did you tell Yi Wei to turn himself in?

