Isn't that the right thing to do?

00:34:35.520 --> 00:34:36.520
Before this,

00:34:36.521 --> 00:34:38.279
all those abnormal behaviors of yours,

00:34:38.280 --> 00:34:40.240
I finally have a reasonable explanation.

00:34:42.360 --> 00:34:43.440
Let me ask you one more thing.

00:34:44.240 --> 00:34:45.760
You'd better be honest with me.

00:34:46.600 --> 00:34:48.560
While covering up for Wei Wei,

00:34:50.000 --> 00:34:51.800
did you do anything illegal?

00:34:52.360 --> 00:34:54.360
Have you ever implicated innocent people?

00:37:12.480 --> 00:37:13.760
I've canceled my leave.

