I just want to clarify a few facts.

00:37:25.120 --> 00:37:26.960
It won't affect the direction of the investigation.

00:37:27.440 --> 00:37:29.720
It's also fairer for your son.

00:37:30.320 --> 00:37:31.320
You don't object, right?

00:37:33.080 --> 00:37:34.080
That day,

00:37:34.160 --> 00:37:35.439
you insisted that Ma Shan Bao...

00:37:35.440 --> 00:37:36.560
was the one who stole the car.

00:37:37.040 --> 00:37:38.040
But now,

00:37:38.240 --> 00:37:39.960
your son turned himself in.

00:37:40.280 --> 00:37:42.160
He said he was the one who hit Han Gang.

