It was the police who identified Ma Shan Bao...

00:37:54.320 --> 00:37:55.320
as the car thief.

00:37:55.320 --> 00:37:56.320
It has nothing to do with me.

00:37:56.600 --> 00:37:57.600
Are you satisfied...

00:37:57.720 --> 00:37:58.720
with this answer?

00:37:59.200 --> 00:38:00.279
I showed you the CCTV photos...

00:38:00.280 --> 00:38:02.040
of Qin Yi Wei at the hospital.

00:38:02.400 --> 00:38:03.400
You promised me...

00:38:03.401 --> 00:38:04.960
you'd bring him in for questioning.

00:38:05.560 --> 00:38:06.560
But not long after that,

00:38:06.720 --> 00:38:08.160
I was reported...

00:38:08.440 --> 00:38:09.560
for an internal investigation.

00:38:10.080 --> 00:38:11.560
The night I asked Han Lie to meet,

00:38:11.760 --> 00:38:12.760
you also asked to meet me.

00:38:13.040 --> 00:38:14.040
You told me...

00:38:14.041 --> 00:38:15.240
you were already in my neighborhood.

00:38:15.720 --> 00:38:16.879
So the person most likely...

00:38:16.880 --> 00:38:18.080
to have seen me meeting with Han Lie...

00:38:18.680 --> 00:38:19.680
was you.

00:38:20.000 --> 00:38:21.359
But the one who reported me...

00:38:21.360 --> 00:38:22.720
was Ms. Zhou Luo Wen.

00:38:23.240 --> 00:38:25.240
Do you really not know anything about all this?

00:38:25.880 --> 00:38:27.480
Was it really just a coincidence?

