As a judge,

00:38:43.560 --> 00:38:44.840
I can't just sit back and do nothing.

00:38:45.200 --> 00:38:47.880
But since this is an informal conversation,

00:38:48.480 --> 00:38:49.720
I can pretend...

00:38:50.000 --> 00:38:51.280
I didn't hear what you just said.

00:38:52.080 --> 00:38:53.240
But I have to remind you.

00:38:53.920 --> 00:38:55.080
Breaching confidentiality...

00:38:55.440 --> 00:38:56.920
is a disciplinary offense.

00:38:58.560 --> 00:39:00.000
Qin Yi Wei's statement...

00:39:00.320 --> 00:39:01.639
clearly stated...

00:39:01.640 --> 00:39:03.320
the time and place of the accident.

00:39:03.880 --> 00:39:05.000
But that night,

00:39:05.200 --> 00:39:06.639
you personally came to the police station...

00:39:06.640 --> 00:39:07.680
and reported the car stolen.

00:39:09.360 --> 00:39:10.360
According to the records,

00:39:10.760 --> 00:39:11.879
you said the car...

00:39:11.880 --> 00:39:13.560
was stolen around 10am.

