How do you know...

00:39:15.320 --> 00:39:16.800
the car was stolen at 10am?

00:39:17.480 --> 00:39:18.920
What I want to know is,

00:39:19.120 --> 00:39:20.120
what's the difference...

00:39:20.440 --> 00:39:22.560
between what you said and the statement...

00:39:22.920 --> 00:39:24.040
your son Qin Yi Wei provided?

